data.title: Gunther Eysenbach - University of Victoria
data.meta_description: Gunther Eysenbach, MD MPH FACMI is founder, executive editor and CEO of JMIR… · Experience: University of Victoria · Location: Toronto · 500+ connections on LinkedIn. View Gunther Eysenbach’s profile on LinkedIn, a professional community of 1 billion members.
data.text:
“Gunther is an outstanding researcher in medical informatics. He has made seminal contributions that are highly cited and have influenced the field. He has increased access to knowledge through his publications and conferences.”

“Congratulations Gunther The new JMIR Impact Factor released in June 2009 is now 3.6 (up from last years' 3.0)! JMIR is now the top ranked, most influential, #1 cited journal in the health informatics category (out of 20 journals), and the #2 journal in the health sciences category (out of 62 leading journals).”
